    "## Retrieve Geoinformation from Vegagerðin's GeoServer API"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "b205dd15-16d9-430f-ad61-1db4aad505a7",
   "metadata": {},
